<h2>
  Amsterdam's Ruby User Group
</h2>
<p>
  We are the Amsterdam Ruby User Group. We exist to promote all aspects of Ruby
  within the area of Amsterdam.
</p>
<p>
  Our aim is to make Amsterdam a centre of excellence for Ruby development.
</p>
<p>
  We meet on the last Monday of every month, and welcome anybody with an
  interest in the language Ruby, or even the framework Rails. We particularly
  welcome newcomers to join our friendly local community to share, teach and
  generate new Ruby knowledge.
</p>
